{"tid":2189571,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"與川普不同調　拜登指美大選最大威脅是俄羅斯非中國","createTime":"2020-09-05T03:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T11:43:32.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"84ff29019940dc57dccf8d59912cfa180bdfbd9e","tid":2189571,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:45:44.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯干預2016美國總統大選疑雲鬧得沸沸揚揚，如今2020總統選舉進入倒數階段，現任總統川普陣營將警戒目標對準中國，認為中國將積極干預大選，但對手民主黨候選人拜登有不同看法，指俄羅斯威脅更勝中國。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，拜登當地時間週五在德拉瓦州向記者表示，他不同意中國是本次總統大選最大威脅的說法，有關分析與他所掌握的情報並不吻合，「我相信世界上有很多國家樂見美國選舉一團亂，當中最努力干預且始終如一的是俄羅斯。」<br />\n<br />\n美國司法部長巴爾（William Barr）近日接受《CNN》訪問時，被問到哪個國家最積極干預美國今年選舉？巴爾回答：「我相信是中國，因為我收到的情資讓我得出了這樣的結論。」美國國安顧問歐布萊恩在白宮記者會上則表示，「是的，我百分之百同意巴爾的說法。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3282342\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3282342&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs429Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=21da26b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3282342&h=5ace604d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3282342</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://nypost.com/2020/09/04/joe-biden-says-russia-not-china-is-top-threat-to-election/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2020%2F09%2F04%2Fjoe-biden-says-russia-not-china-is-top-threat-to-election%2F&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs429Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=1a3ad432\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nypost.com/2020/09/04/joe-biden-says-russia-not-china-is-top-threat-to-election/</a>"},{"pid":"c6904f7fa04875a455eb181f0d9c90857062a1d1","tid":2189571,"uid":21545,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:46:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" cl